@startuml
title Activity Diagram FR-13: Maintenance / OOS

|Lab Asset Manager|
start
:Access asset management;
:Select hardware asset;

|System|
:Display asset details;

|Lab Asset Manager|
:Choose new status;

if (Status to set?) then (Out of Service)
    :Enter OOS reason;
    :Enter expected return date;
    
    |System|
    :Update asset status to OOS;
    :Remove from available assets list;
    :Add OOS banner to asset info page;
    :Display confirmation;
    
    stop
    
else (Available)
    |System|
    if (Current status is OOS?) then (yes)
        :Update asset status to Available;
        :Add to available assets list;
        :Remove OOS banner;
        :Display confirmation;
        
        stop
    else (no)
        :Display error: Asset is already Available;
        
        stop
    endif
endif

@enduml
